        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4152",
        "content": "A PORTRAIT FROM LIFE",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4152_12926_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4152/12926/4152_12926_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4152",
        "content": "This young man with a livid face-a blonde of the type with black eyes, whose immovable glance has an indescribable fascination, sober in speech as in conduct, dressed in black, lean as a consumptive, but nevertheless vigorously framed-visited the family of his former master and the house of his cashier less from affection than from self interest.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4152_12926_000004_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4152/12926/4152_12926_000004_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4152",
        "content": "The young fellow looked at Modeste precisely as he would have looked at a cheap lithograph.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4152_12926_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4152/12926/4152_12926_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4152",
        "content": "His little eyes, of a calm blue, were like bits of steel.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4152_12926_000009_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4152/12926/4152_12926_000009_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4152",
        "content": "His physical strength, well-known to every one, put him above all danger of attack.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4152_12926_000010_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4152/12926/4152_12926_000010_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4152",
        "content": "Her face expressed the pleasure she took in the smooth petals of the flower she was working.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4152_12926_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4152/12926/4152_12926_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4152",
        "content": "It was eight o'clock.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4152_12926_000012_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4152/12926/4152_12926_000012_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4152",
        "content": "Modeste,--blossom enclosed, like that of Catullus,--was she worth all these precautions?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4152_12926_000013_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4152/12926/4152_12926_000013_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4152",
        "content": "It seemed, like a pearl, to have its orient.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4152_5710_000002_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4152/5710/4152_5710_000002_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4152",
        "content": "Admission to the class is gained by exercise of the pecuniary aptitudes-aptitudes for acquisition rather than for serviceability. There is, therefore, a continued selective sifting of the human material that makes up the leisure class, and this selection proceeds on the ground of fitness for pecuniary pursuits.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4152_5710_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4152/5710/4152_5710_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4152",
        "content": "The most immediate and unequivocal expression of that archaic human nature which characterizes man in the predatory stage is the fighting propensity proper.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4152_5710_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4152/5710/4152_5710_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4152",
        "content": "In cases where the predatory activity is a collective one, this propensity is frequently called the martial spirit, or, latterly, patriotism.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4152_5710_000003_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4152/5710/4152_5710_000003_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4152",
        "content": "Indeed, the leisure class claims the distinction as a matter of pride, and no doubt with some grounds.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4152_5710_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4152/5710/4152_5710_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4152",
        "content": "In the male child the predaceous interval is ordinarily fairly well marked and lasts for some time, but it is commonly terminated (if at all) with the attainment of maturity.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4152_5710_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4152/5710/4152_5710_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4152",
        "content": "This last statement may need very material qualification.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4152_5710_000014_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4152/5710/4152_5710_000014_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4152",
        "content": "The same is true of the encouragement given to the growth of \"college spirit,\" college athletics, and the like, in the higher institutions of learning.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
